name: The Mystery v5 (tower), (Eternity Render 4)
description: This is a simulation of the sculpture The Mystery v5 (tower), which is a physical sculpture created for the 4 person exhibition, "So Excited!", which occurwd at Steve Turner LA gallery in August of 2021. The Mystery v5 is a talisman in the style of Baroque memento mori. This is 4 in a series of 5 renders of this digital sculpture. This version is made of translucent pink resin and pure silver presented on mirror. PNG file, 2480 x 3508 pixels
